ow/|title=The Windsors Season 4: Release Date, Cast, Plot and Everything You Need To Know.|last=Ghosh|first=Joydeep|date=2020-04-05|website=OtakuKart News|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.comedy.co.uk/people/andrew_bridgmont/|title=Andrew Bridgmont|last=Guide|first=British Comedy|website=British Comedy Guide|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|-\n![[Grantchester (TV series)|Grandchester]]\n|2020\n|Douglas Munroe\n|Season 5, Episode 4 directed by Christiana Ebohon.\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Episode #5.4|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt11082368/|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|-\n![[Howards End (miniseries)|Howards End]]\n|2017\n|Swanage Doctor\n|Season 1, Episode 4 directed by [[Hettie Macdonald]].\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Episode #1.4|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt6691798/|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|-\n![[The Halcyon]]\n|2017\n|Doctor\n|Season 1, Episode 4 directed by Rob Evans.\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Episode #1.4|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt5821318/|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|-\n![[Penny Dreadful (TV series)|Penny Dreadful]]\n|2016\n|Ship Doctor\n|Season 3, Episode 1 titled: ''\"The Day Tennyson Died\"'' directed by Damon Thomas.\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=The Day Tennyson Died|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt4786300/|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|-\n![[Houdini & Doyle]]\n|2016\n|Dr. Perlow\n|Season 1, Episode 3 titled: ''\"In Manus Dei\"'' directed by Daniel O'Hara.\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=In Manus Dei|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt5168370/|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|-\n![[The Frankenstein Chronicles]]\n|2015\n|Librarian\n|Season 1, Episode 2 directed by [[Benjamin Ross]].\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Seeing Things|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt4510234/|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|-\n![[Party Animals (TV series)|Party Animals]]\n|2007\n|Marcus Walter\n|Season 1, Episode 2 directed by Brian Grant.\n|<ref>{{Citation|title=Episode #1.2|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0966370/|access-da