den.nl/charts/swedish%20charts/SwedishCharts%200969-0872.pdf \"Swedish Charts 1969\u20131972/Kv\u00e4llstoppen \u2013 Listresultaten vecka f\u00f6r vecka\" > Februari 1971 > 9 Februari] (in Swedish), hitsallertijden.nl (retrieved 13 February 2013). ''Note: [[Sverigetopplistan|Kv\u00e4llstoppen]] combined sales for albums and singles in the one chart; ''All Things Must Pass'' topped the albums listings for six weeks from 2 February to 9 March 1971.''</ref>\n|1\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" align=\"left\"|[[UK Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"UKchart\" />\n|1\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" align=\"left\"|US [[Billboard 200|''Billboard'' Top LPs]]<ref name=\"USchart\">[http://www.allmusic.com/artist/george-harrison-mn0000209142/awards \"All Things Must Pass\" > Charts & Awards > Billboard Albums], [[AllMusic]] (retrieved 11 February 2013).</ref>\n|1\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" align=\"left\"|US ''[[Cash Box (magazine)|Cash Box]]'' Top 100 Albums<ref>\"Cash Box Top 100 Albums\", ''[[Cash Box (magazine)|Cash Box]]'', 9 January 1971, p. 21.</ref>\n|1\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" align=\"left\"|US ''[[Record World]]'' Album Chart<ref>Frank Mitchell (ed.), \"The Album Chart\", ''[[Record World]]'', 16 January 1971, p. 30.</ref>\n|1\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" align=\"left\"|West German [[Media Control Charts|Media Control Albums]]<ref name=\"dechart\">[http://www.officialcharts.de/album.asp?artist=George+Harrison&title=All+Things+Must+Pass&country=de \"Album \u2013 George Harrison, All Things Must Pass\"], charts.de (retrieved 11 February 2013).</ref>\n|10\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n'''Reissue'''\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"|Chart (2001)\n! scope=\"col\"|Position\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" align=\"left\"|French [[SNEP|SNEP Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"snep\">[https://web.archive.org/web/20150509014530/http://www.infodisc.fr/Albums_Detail.php \"Tous les Albums class\u00e9s par Artiste\" > Choisir un Artiste dans la Liste] (in French), infodisc.fr (archive version retrieved 13 February 201